P1.15, P1.16, P1.17 Configuration Changes
==========================================

P1.15 Default Docker Image (nginx:latest removed):
- createTaskDefinition now returns error if imageRef is empty
- Line ~1067: if strings.TrimSpace(imageRef) == '' returns error
- Users must explicitly specify image_ref

P1.16 Log Retention Hardcoded (now configurable):
- Added LogRetentionDays to createInfraInput
- provisionLogGroup accepts logRetentionDays parameter
- Defaults to 7 if not specified or <= 0
- Valid CloudWatch values: 1,3,5,7,14,30,60,90,120,150,180,365...

P1.17 ECS Task Resources Hardcoded (now configurable):
- Added CPU and Memory to deployInput
- createTaskDefinition accepts cpu, memory parameters
- Defaults: CPU='256', Memory='512'
- Users can specify Fargate-compatible combinations

Schema documentation in jsonschema tags guides users to valid values.
